# 1️⃣1️⃣ POST-AWARD DATA LOCKING

After award:

* Evaluation data frozen
* Scores immutable
* Justifications archived
* Price intelligence snapshot stored
* Audit trail sealed

Prevents retroactive manipulation.

---

